name: PhysiCell
description: A physics-based cell simulator that models 3D multicellular systems, focusing on the interactions of (off-lattice) cells with their microenvironment.

processes.name: CellProliferation
processes.description: Process describing the proliferation and division of cells.

processes.name: CellMigration
processes.description: Process describing the movement of cells within the microenvironment.

processes.name: CellDeath
processes.description: Process describing programmed cell death (apoptosis) and necrosis.
